$interpreted: Himawari: You sure you don't want to run back and avoid the tournament like the rest of your team? You don't need to throw your life away.
Miranda: Seems to me like you're the one who's hiding.
Miranda: If it weren't for the tournament, I doubt I'd ever have had this chance to take you head on!
Himawari: You actually think you could beat me right now?
Miranda: Won't know if we don't try.
Chiyuki: Ladies and gentlemen, the first round of the Martial Arts Tournament, Miranda versus Himawari...
Chiyuki: begins now!
Miranda: (Grrr--!!)
Himawari: (Hmph, she's bleeding... Let's see how long she can hold up.)
Himawari: (She's got no air left! Time to finish this!)
Chiyuki: Looks like they're both at the end of their ropes, ladies and gentlemen. How about we see who can grab this one last oxygen herb!
Himawari: (Another oxygen herb! I've got to get it!)
Himawari: (She's too slow! How does she expect to win with that speed? This oxygen herb is mine!)
Himawari: (You're too far! What are you reaching for!?)
Himawari: (Eh!? She's grabbing my tail!?)
Himawari: (Wait a second, is she trying to—)
Miranda: (Sorry Himawari, but you lose~)
Surprised Viewer: Eh!? She pulled her down by the tail!!
Scared Viewer: Hold on, is her tail... melting!?
Surprised Viewer: Not just her tail, her whole—

Ace: ...Her fur's gone, but there's no blood, just that light... 
Could it have been rune magic?
Shun: Who the... Is that Himawari!?
Surprised Viewer: She's got no fur! She's a human! A human!!
Himawari: Don't look at me...
Juan-Yun: Don't be scared, Himawari.
Himawari: Juan... Juan-Yun.
Juan-Yun: Don't worry, I've got you. They can't see you.
Himawari: I'm so sorry, Juan-Yun. I've lied to you... You've been so good to me, I didn't mean to...
Juan-Yun: Shh... It's all right. Everything's okay.
Scared Viewer: Hey, the other human's passed out! She's gonna drown!
Tindoiimu: It's clear who's won, why isn't she announcing it?
Chiyuki: And the winner is... Himawari!!
Toyokuni: The victor has been announced... Soohyeon, can you save her?
Soohyeon: Okay!
Maeok: ...So who's going to tell me what the heck is going on?
